---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import ContactForm from '../../components/ContactForm.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Bulverde Neighborhoods | Cody Posey Real Estate"
  description="Explore Bulverde, TX neighborhoods by community and price range. Find the right fit for your lifestyle and budget in the Hill Country."
>
  <Navbar />
  <main style="padding-top: 80px;">

    <!-- Hero -->
    <div class="bv-hero">
      <div class="bv-hero__overlay"></div>
      <div class="bv-hero__content">
        <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
          <a href="/">Home</a> <span>/</span> <a href="/bulverde/">Bulverde</a> <span>/</span> <span>Neighborhoods</span>
        </nav>
        <h1>Bulverde <span style="color:#FF1616;">Neighborhoods</span></h1>
        <p>Find the right community for your lifestyle and budget</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Intro -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="bv-page-intro bv-page-intro--centered">Bulverde offers a range of neighborhoods — from master-planned communities with full amenities to quiet subdivisions on larger lots. All are served by Comal ISD and share the area's Hill Country character.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Neighborhoods -->
    <section class="section" style="background: var(--light-gray);">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
          <h2>Bulverde <span class="accent">Communities</span></h2>
        </div>

        <div class="bv-area">
          <h3>Estates at Indian Springs</h3>
          <div class="bv-area__meta">
            <span class="bv-area__price">$400K - $700K</span>
            <span class="bv-area__district">Comal ISD</span>
          </div>
          <p>Large lots and custom-style homes define this established community. Estates at Indian Springs appeals to buyers looking for space, privacy, and a Hill Country setting with room to spread out. Lot sizes here are generous compared to more densely developed neighborhoods closer to the city.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bv-area">
          <h3>Bulverde Village</h3>
          <div class="bv-area__meta">
            <span class="bv-area__price">$350K - $550K</span>
            <span class="bv-area__district">Comal ISD</span>
          </div>
          <p>Conveniently located near schools and local services, Bulverde Village offers a family-friendly environment with easy access to the essentials. The community balances a neighborhood feel with proximity to Bulverde's main corridors.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bv-area">
          <h3>Hidden Trails</h3>
          <div class="bv-area__meta">
            <span class="bv-area__price">$200K - $400K</span>
            <span class="bv-area__district">Comal ISD</span>
          </div>
          <p>A more accessible price point with well-built brick homes and a quiet, established feel. Hidden Trails is a solid option for first-time buyers and families looking for value in the Bulverde area without sacrificing the Hill Country lifestyle.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bv-area">
          <h3>Johnson Ranch</h3>
          <div class="bv-area__meta">
            <span class="bv-area__price">$350K - $600K</span>
            <span class="bv-area__district">Comal ISD</span>
          </div>
          <p>A master-planned community with resort-style amenities including pools, parks, and trails. Johnson Ranch attracts families and move-up buyers who want a neighborhood with built-in lifestyle features and a strong sense of community.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bv-area">
          <h3>Singing Hills</h3>
          <div class="bv-area__meta">
            <span class="bv-area__price">$300K - $500K</span>
            <span class="bv-area__district">Comal ISD</span>
          </div>
          <p>Hill Country views and a peaceful setting make Singing Hills a popular choice for buyers who prioritize scenery and a quieter pace. The community offers a mix of home styles with the rolling terrain that defines the Bulverde landscape.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- School District -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
          <h2>School <span class="accent">District</span></h2>
          <p>Bulverde is served by one of the top districts in the Hill Country</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bv-schools__grid">
          <a href="https://www.comalisd.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="bv-schools__card">
            <h3>Comal ISD</h3>
            <p>One of the fastest-growing districts in Texas, Comal ISD serves the entire Bulverde area. The district is known for strong academics, modern facilities, and a wide range of extracurricular programs.</p>
            <span class="bv-schools__link">Visit Comal ISD Website →</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="section" style="background: #000; color: #fff; text-align: center;">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Need Help <span class="accent">Narrowing It Down</span>?</h2>
        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); max-width: 600px; margin: 1rem auto 2rem;">I can walk you through the differences between Bulverde communities and help you focus your search on neighborhoods that match your priorities.</p>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-outline">Get Help Narrowing Down Areas</a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  <ContactForm context="I need help narrowing down Bulverde neighborhoods..." />
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .bv-hero {
    position: relative;
    height: 280px;
    background: #000;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .bv-hero__overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000 0%, #1a0000 100%);
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .bv-hero__content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .bv-hero__content h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .bv-hero__content p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .breadcrumb {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  }

  .breadcrumb a {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .breadcrumb a:hover {
    color: #FF1616;
  }

  .breadcrumb span {
    margin: 0 0.3rem;
  }

  .bv-page-intro {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--gray);
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .bv-page-intro--centered {
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--black);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Area Cards */
  .bv-area {
    background: #fff;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }

  .bv-area h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .bv-area__meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .bv-area__price {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #FF1616;
  }

  .bv-area__district {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--gray);
    background: var(--light-gray);
    padding: 0.15rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .bv-area p {
    color: var(--gray);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .bv-area p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Schools */
  .bv-schools__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .bv-schools__card {
    display: block;
    background: #fff;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .bv-schools__card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .bv-schools__card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: #000;
  }

  .bv-schools__card:hover h3 {
    color: #FF1616;
  }

  .bv-schools__card p {
    color: var(--gray);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .bv-schools__link {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: #FF1616;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .bv-area__meta {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
